1
00:01:30,128 --> 00:01:32,808
[Episode 35]

2
00:01:33,342 --> 00:01:35,754
You arbitrarily expanded the army under your control.

3
00:01:35,754 --> 00:01:37,505
By placing your army here today,

4
00:01:37,505 --> 00:01:40,651
your intention to usurp power and revolt is as clear as day.

5
00:01:40,651 --> 00:01:43,940
How could you face those soldiers who have followed you so loyally...

6
00:01:43,940 --> 00:01:46,820
and the people of Northern Lin who have trusted and respected you?

7
00:01:46,820 --> 00:01:50,269
General Fu, where's your conscience?

8
00:01:50,269 --> 00:01:52,469
Where's my conscience?

9
00:01:54,820 --> 00:01:56,700
Today, I'm not afraid to say that...

10
00:01:56,700 --> 00:02:01,020
I have a clear conscience towards every person in Northern Lin.

11
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:04,100
I would like to ask you instead.

12
00:02:04,100 --> 00:02:06,284
When I'm fighting on the battlefield,

13
00:02:06,284 --> 00:02:09,555
what contributions have you given them?

14
00:02:09,555 --> 00:02:12,412
Now, you claim that you've put down the rebellion...

15
00:02:12,412 --> 00:02:14,843
at the southern border as a prince.

16
00:02:15,460 --> 00:02:17,620
Do you think that by doing so,

17
00:02:17,620 --> 00:02:20,085
you can shadow the world with your merits...

18
00:02:20,085 --> 00:02:22,934
and you can plead on the people's behalf?

19
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:27,579
I don't care at all... about your opinion of me.

20
00:02:29,540 --> 00:02:32,500
Since you've no regrets about the crime that you've committed,

21
00:02:32,500 --> 00:02:35,060
I've brought along my army to the palace.

22
00:02:35,060 --> 00:02:39,775
I'm going to get rid of a traitor like you with ill intention...

23
00:02:39,775 --> 00:02:42,700
for those innocent people and soldiers who were sacrificed...

24
00:02:42,700 --> 00:02:46,282
at the southern border rebellion and for my father who had died in vain.

25
00:02:46,282 --> 00:02:49,977
Looks like you are going to take the position...

26
00:02:49,977 --> 00:02:52,017
as crown prince by force.

27
00:02:52,017 --> 00:02:54,251
But I am different from you.

28
00:02:54,251 --> 00:02:58,981
After all these years, I'm already sick of all the slaughter.

29
00:02:58,981 --> 00:03:04,422
Of course, I believe that you are not willing to sacrifice your soldiers from the southern border either.

30
00:03:05,340 --> 00:03:07,168
- Guard.
- Yes, General.

31
00:03:07,168 --> 00:03:09,999
- Bring my wife here.
- Yes, General.

32
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:22,017
Man Yao.

33
00:03:57,900 --> 00:04:00,088
From the way you look,

34
00:04:00,088 --> 00:04:02,720
are you going to take away my wife again today?

35
00:04:03,148 --> 00:04:04,495
How about you take a guess.

36
00:04:04,495 --> 00:04:08,012
Do you think I'll let you succeed today?

37
00:04:08,012 --> 00:04:10,025
If you really treat her as your wife,

38
00:04:10,025 --> 00:04:12,088
you wouldn't drag her into such a dangerous situation.

39
00:04:12,089 --> 00:04:13,860
It's not up to you or me to decide.

40
00:04:13,860 --> 00:04:16,820
It's entirely up to her.

41
00:04:19,740 --> 00:04:23,314
Are you willing to marry me?

42
00:04:28,229 --> 00:04:30,109
I'm willing.

43
00:04:39,158 --> 00:04:43,143
The daughter of Central Secretary, Sun Yali... is virtuous and pure.

44
00:04:43,143 --> 00:04:46,599
She is very affectionate towards me... and cares for me.

45
00:04:46,599 --> 00:04:50,099
So, I've decided that after today, I'm going to take her as a wife.

46
00:04:50,099 --> 00:04:53,048
And I vow that... she'll be my only wife in this life.

47
00:04:53,048 --> 00:04:55,539
I won't have another ever again.

48
00:04:59,076 --> 00:05:01,736
You won't divorce Man Yao so easily.

49
00:05:01,736 --> 00:05:03,333
Where is she?

50
00:05:04,460 --> 00:05:09,868
Prince Li, since you care about the woman that I've thrown away,

51
00:05:09,868 --> 00:05:13,060
I'll give this woman to you.

52
00:05:14,180 --> 00:05:17,521
Let's see if you are willing to accept this gift.

53
00:06:36,060 --> 00:06:38,360
What did you do to her?

54
00:06:41,740 --> 00:06:45,821
She is poisoned by... Scorpion Toxin.

55
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:47,906
Those who are poisoned...

56
00:06:47,906 --> 00:06:51,874
will suffer as if their whole bodies were being burned by wildfire.

57
00:06:51,874 --> 00:06:54,630
It will call upon her deepest hatred.

58
00:06:54,630 --> 00:06:57,359
Her mind will freeze as if it is encased in ice.

59
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:59,020
As soon as it freezes,

60
00:06:59,020 --> 00:07:01,606
the mind will be swallowed by hatred.

61
00:07:01,606 --> 00:07:03,458
She will lose all conscience.

62
00:07:57,612 --> 00:07:59,790
I suggest that you hold yourself back first.

63
00:07:59,790 --> 00:08:03,780
Since I've already made my promise, I won't go back on my words.

64
00:08:03,780 --> 00:08:05,822
If you act recklessly again,

65
00:08:05,823 --> 00:08:09,253
the only thing you will get is a dead body.

66
