73
00:08:55,117 --> 00:08:59,420
Today, it is not me or Man Yao who loses our faces in public.

74
00:08:59,420 --> 00:09:00,810
It's you.

75
00:09:00,810 --> 00:09:03,573
You are a despicable and cunning low life.

76
00:09:04,140 --> 00:09:06,800
You still don't understand.

77
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:11,259
Do you know who the oneis that caused all of this?

78
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:16,031
When I married Rong Le, I've never thought of using her to threaten you.

79
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:21,700
It turned out like this today... because of you.

80
00:09:21,700 --> 00:09:23,743
You kidnapped her on our wedding day.

81
00:09:23,743 --> 00:09:25,780
And you admitted in public...

82
00:09:25,780 --> 00:09:29,399
that you had an amorous past with Rong Le.

83
00:09:29,399 --> 00:09:30,919
Then, you took her away...

84
00:09:30,920 --> 00:09:33,729
and locked her in the Yun Mausoleum for three days and three nights.

85
00:09:33,729 --> 00:09:37,620
Later on, you repeatedly barged into my manor to take her away by force.

86
00:09:37,620 --> 00:09:41,780
Prince Li, when you took all of those unscrupulous actions,

87
00:09:41,780 --> 00:09:45,080
you should have known that as her husband,

88
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:49,052
this is how I was going to treat her for your actions.

89
00:09:49,052 --> 00:09:51,100
The endless sufferings that I had...

90
00:09:51,100 --> 00:09:53,697
and the pain that Rong Le is in today...

91
00:09:53,697 --> 00:09:57,077
are caused single-handedly by you, Zongzheng Wuyou.

92
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:03,300
Now, she is poisoned with Scorpion Toxin.

93
00:10:03,300 --> 00:10:04,925
She has only one hour left.

94
00:10:04,925 --> 00:10:08,273
If she doesn't consume the cure in an hour's time,

95
00:10:08,273 --> 00:10:12,687
then you'll have to watch while she dies in pain.

96
00:10:25,420 --> 00:10:27,340
As long as you promise...

97
00:10:27,340 --> 00:10:30,840
not to harm the innocent lives of the southern border soldiers behind me...

98
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:33,586
and are willing to give me the cure,

99
00:10:33,587 --> 00:10:35,367
