122
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:10,139
Princess Rong Le once treated me as her friend.

123
00:12:10,139 --> 00:12:12,599
I'm in debt with Prince Li as well.

124
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:16,418
If you really have me in your heart,

125
00:12:16,419 --> 00:12:19,416
you'll let go of them for me.

126
00:12:25,210 --> 00:12:27,159
You once told me that...

127
00:12:27,160 --> 00:12:29,815
you'll stand by my side forever.

128
00:12:29,815 --> 00:12:32,520
But you plead for them today.

129
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:35,159
If I let go of them today, do you think that...

130
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:36,920
they'll let go of me in the future?

131
00:12:36,921 --> 00:12:40,217
Sun Yali, do you wish to see me...

132
00:12:40,217 --> 00:12:43,703
falling into the abyss as well?

133
00:12:49,251 --> 00:12:53,177
Guards. Bring her away.

134
00:12:53,177 --> 00:12:54,817
Yes, General.

135
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:06,005
Zongzheng Wuyou, let me remind you again.

136
00:13:06,005 --> 00:13:08,059
One hour's time is almost up.

137
00:13:08,059 --> 00:13:11,728
Are you going to surrender or not?

138
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:23,500
Wuyou.

139
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:25,240
Wuyu.

140
00:13:26,680 --> 00:13:29,359
Remember what I told you today.

141
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:33,039
No matter what happens, don't disobey me.

142
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:36,640
Promise me.

143
00:13:36,640 --> 00:13:38,639
If things go wrong today,

144
00:13:38,640 --> 00:13:40,680
the lives of the soldiers and the people will be your priority.

145
00:13:40,681 --> 00:13:42,721
Keep your strength.

146
00:13:42,721 --> 00:13:45,741
Wuyou, I promise you.

147
00:13:48,520 --> 00:13:50,640
Yes, Wuyou.

148
00:13:53,540 --> 00:13:55,899
Today, we are here tosettle our old scores.

149
00:13:55,899 --> 00:13:58,110
I'll bear it alone.

150
00:13:58,111 --> 00:14:00,519
Wuyu has neither grievance nor rancor against you.

151
00:14:00,520 --> 00:14:03,220
I believe that you won't make things difficult for him.

152
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:07,379
What I want is for you...

153
00:14:07,379 --> 00:14:10,008
to kneel and surrender to me.

154
00:14:11,700 --> 00:14:14,280
- Leng Yan.
- Yes, Your Highness.

155
00:14:15,180 --> 00:14:17,119
