156
00:14:17,120 --> 00:14:18,300
Yes!

157
00:14:18,300 --> 00:14:20,150
Your Highness Prince Chen.

158
00:14:21,740 --> 00:14:26,220
Wuyou, I'll take my leave now.

159
00:14:50,200 --> 00:14:52,696
No!

160
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:58,639
Don't, Wuyou!

161
00:14:58,640 --> 00:15:00,999
I'd rather die!

162
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:05,423
Man Yao, please forgive me for my wayward way once more.

163
00:15:21,040 --> 00:15:25,100
I... surrender.

164
00:15:42,040 --> 00:15:46,168
This is the only bottle of cure that can save Rong Le.

165
00:15:46,168 --> 00:15:49,759
Zongzheng Wuyou, you've always been arrogant and proud.

166
00:15:49,759 --> 00:15:52,111
You've never respected anybody else.

167
00:15:52,112 --> 00:15:55,797
