251
00:25:32,836 --> 00:25:35,404
Although it has been neutralized, her body is heavily damaged.

252
00:25:35,404 --> 00:25:36,810
This is inevitable.

253
00:25:36,810 --> 00:25:39,352
Get along with it then! Quick!

254
00:26:18,638 --> 00:26:20,625
What should I do?

255
00:26:22,312 --> 00:26:25,390
It wasn't supposed to be you. I'd asked Hen Xiang...

256
00:26:25,390 --> 00:26:27,594
I've asked Hen Xiang to take your place.

257
00:26:28,740 --> 00:26:31,134
Why did it become the real you?

258
00:26:32,080 --> 00:26:35,380
What should I do?

259
00:26:41,348 --> 00:26:43,308
Atone for my sin.

260
00:26:48,911 --> 00:26:52,522
The only thing I can do for the rest of my life is to atone for my sin.

261
00:26:52,522 --> 00:26:54,686
I need to atone for my sin.

262
00:26:58,520 --> 00:27:02,139
General Fu, we still have important things to do.

263
00:27:02,139 --> 00:27:06,085
General Fu.

264
00:27:06,085 --> 00:27:08,090
Important things.

265
00:27:11,440 --> 00:27:13,341
Important things.

266
00:27:15,205 --> 00:27:18,849
Chang Jian. Chang Jian.

267
00:27:18,849 --> 00:27:21,993
Chang Jian! What are the important things?

268
00:27:21,993 --> 00:27:24,880
Tell me! What are the important things?

269
00:27:25,614 --> 00:27:29,039
Chang Jian, I'd replaced Rong Le with Hen Xiang.

270
00:27:29,039 --> 00:27:31,713
Why did it become the real Rong Le? Why?

271
00:27:31,713 --> 00:27:33,534
Why?

272
00:27:57,936 --> 00:27:59,496
Quick!

273
00:28:01,120 --> 00:28:03,619
- Quick!
- Your Highness, General Fu is outside.

274
00:28:03,619 --> 00:28:05,004
Good.

275
00:28:05,004 --> 00:28:08,812
Good. General Fu didn't disappoint me after all.

276
00:28:08,812 --> 00:28:11,833
Call him in!

277
00:28:11,833 --> 00:28:16,481
Come in, General of Defense, Fu Chou.

278
00:28:26,263 --> 00:28:28,063
General Fu!

279
00:28:30,322 --> 00:28:34,373
General Fu. General Fu.

280
00:28:34,373 --> 00:28:38,200
General Fu, you are indeed the pillar of Northern Lin,

281
00:28:38,200 --> 00:28:40,654
the right-hand man that I rely on.

282
00:28:40,654 --> 00:28:43,715
Don't worry. I'll have a feast for the army.

283
00:28:43,715 --> 00:28:45,722
And I'll reward them accordingly.

284
00:28:45,722 --> 00:28:47,503
Come here.

285
00:28:49,080 --> 00:28:50,599
General Fu.

286
00:28:50,599 --> 00:28:52,099
Pass on my order.

287
00:28:52,099 --> 00:28:54,359
Add ten thousand soldiers to guard the inside and outside of the palace.

288
00:28:54,359 --> 00:28:56,726
Nobody can go out without my decree.

289
00:28:56,726 --> 00:28:59,387
Besides, get me ten thousands archers...

290
00:28:59,387 --> 00:29:01,504
to surround the whole of Zhongshan city.

291
00:29:01,504 --> 00:29:05,010
If there are any suspicious or unidentifiable people, kill them.

292
00:29:05,010 --> 00:29:09,440
- Yes, General!
- Good. Get on with it then!

293
00:29:09,440 --> 00:29:11,770
Great! General Fu.

294
00:29:11,770 --> 00:29:13,639
You are indeed a brilliant strategist.

295
00:29:13,639 --> 00:29:16,510
You've turned danger into safety, my great general.

296
00:29:16,510 --> 00:29:18,251
Chang Jian!

297
00:29:21,520 --> 00:29:23,140
General Fu.

298
00:29:29,030 --> 00:29:33,454
Crown Prince... is traitorous, fatuous, and incompetent.

299
00:29:33,454 --> 00:29:35,462
He sells titles and ranks in secret...

300
00:29:35,462 --> 00:29:37,519
and causes disorder in the court.

301
00:29:37,519 --> 00:29:41,177
This is... the evidence of your crime.

302
00:29:48,400 --> 00:29:50,804
The late emperor had asked you to hold the fort.

303
00:29:50,804 --> 00:29:54,078
But you indulged in having fun and slacked off with court affairs.

304
00:29:54,078 --> 00:29:57,019
That's why it turned out like this today.

305
00:29:57,019 --> 00:29:59,268
The crimes that you have committed are endless.

306
00:29:59,268 --> 00:30:01,151
You should be punished to death.

307
00:30:01,151 --> 00:30:02,496
Guards.

308
00:30:02,496 --> 00:30:03,759
Yes, General.

309
00:30:03,759 --> 00:30:07,216
Lock the crown prince up in the Eastern Palace and wait for further orders.

310
00:30:07,216 --> 00:30:08,757
Roger that.

311
00:30:11,740 --> 00:30:13,760
Nonsense!

312
00:30:15,195 --> 00:30:18,342
What nonsense! Nonsense!

313
00:30:18,342 --> 00:30:21,981
Fu Chou! How dare you!

314
00:30:21,981 --> 00:30:24,959
A low life! A traitor!

315
00:30:24,959 --> 00:30:27,179
You've pushed me into a trap that you've laid out!

316
00:30:27,179 --> 00:30:28,680
Release me!

317
00:30:28,680 --> 00:30:32,233
I am the crown prince. This is my country!

318
00:30:34,168 --> 00:30:35,708
Wait!

319
00:30:36,923 --> 00:30:39,819
Your action is quite inappropriate here, General Fu.

320
00:30:39,819 --> 00:30:42,361
Even if the crown prince has made a lot of mistakes,

321
00:30:42,361 --> 00:30:44,798
we are still his subjects.

322
00:30:44,798 --> 00:30:46,319
This...

323
00:30:50,198 --> 00:30:53,095
You asked me about what rights I had.

324
00:30:55,285 --> 00:31:00,084
I have the rights because I am the son of the late empress, Fu Yuan.

325
00:31:01,400 --> 00:31:04,540
- Son of Fu Yuan?
- Is that so?

326
00:31:05,500 --> 00:31:06,819
Is that so?

327
00:31:06,819 --> 00:31:08,639
According to the rule of the ancestors,

328
00:31:08,639 --> 00:31:12,100
the eldest son of the empress will be the true Crown Prince.

329
00:31:12,100 --> 00:31:15,863
If my mother wasn't banished from the palace because of some traitors,

330
00:31:15,863 --> 00:31:19,120
you wouldn't be the crown prince of today.

331
00:31:19,120 --> 00:31:20,561
You...

332
00:31:20,561 --> 00:31:22,316
Nonsense!

333
00:31:22,316 --> 00:31:24,162
There is no proof.

334
00:31:24,162 --> 00:31:27,970
Fu Chou, how dare you pretend to be the son of the royalty.

335
00:31:27,970 --> 00:31:30,111
How bold of you!

336
00:31:30,111 --> 00:31:32,333
You are just a traitor.

337
00:31:32,333 --> 00:31:36,636
You...You are just a traitor!

338
00:31:36,636 --> 00:31:40,409
- Release me!
- Since all officials are here today,

339
00:31:40,409 --> 00:31:43,144
I'll make things clear.

340
00:31:43,144 --> 00:31:45,300
I'm the son of the late empress, Fu Yuan.

341
00:31:45,300 --> 00:31:48,730
The Golden Scroll and Phoenix Seal will prove that.

342
00:31:48,730 --> 00:31:51,485
When the late emperor enthroned the empress,

343
00:31:51,485 --> 00:31:57,252
he told the world that the eldest son of my mother will be given the title of Crown Prince...

344
00:31:57,252 --> 00:31:59,384
and become the successor to the throne.

345
00:31:59,384 --> 00:32:01,264
And it's a promise not to be changed.

346
00:32:02,106 --> 00:32:03,670
Fake.

347
00:32:03,670 --> 00:32:07,077
Fake! Those are fake!

348
00:32:08,152 --> 00:32:09,951
Fake.

349
00:32:35,300 --> 00:32:37,219
After verifying them,

350
00:32:37,219 --> 00:32:40,404
the Golden Scroll and Phoenix Seal are real.

351
00:32:40,404 --> 00:32:43,079
- But...
- But?

352
00:32:43,079 --> 00:32:44,736
But what?

353
00:32:44,736 --> 00:32:48,177
If Sir Yang can't speak it out, let me do it then.

354
00:32:48,177 --> 00:32:51,414
Everybody knows that Empress Fu and her son had passed away.

355
00:32:51,414 --> 00:32:55,381
His Majesty had told us himself. All of us here are witnesses to that.

356
00:32:55,381 --> 00:32:58,764
General Fu, you have the Golden Scroll and Phoenix Seal.

357
00:32:58,764 --> 00:33:02,763
But they can't prove that you are of royal blood.

358
00:33:02,763 --> 00:33:05,479
That's right. You are a fake.

359
00:33:05,479 --> 00:33:07,599
Fu Chou, how bold you are.

360
00:33:07,599 --> 00:33:09,499
How dare you pretend to be the son of royalty!

361
00:33:09,499 --> 00:33:12,087
Guards, arrest him!

362
00:33:12,087 --> 00:33:14,648
Arrest him!

363
00:33:14,648 --> 00:33:19,436
From time immemorial, a traitor will never work alone.

364
00:33:19,436 --> 00:33:24,112
He will have accomplices from the inside and outside of the palace and the court.

365
00:33:24,112 --> 00:33:26,187
Sir Lin.

366
00:33:26,187 --> 00:33:28,460
If I remember correctly,

367
00:33:28,460 --> 00:33:29,983
when my mother was still alive,

368
00:33:29,983 --> 00:33:33,400
she was protective towards you and she doted on you.

369
00:33:33,400 --> 00:33:36,552
You are a second-rank official.

370
00:33:36,552 --> 00:33:38,119
When my mother was accused wrongly,

371
00:33:38,119 --> 00:33:40,601
you didn't step up to defend her.

372
00:33:40,601 --> 00:33:41,907
I don't blame you for that.

373
00:33:41,907 --> 00:33:45,963
Because I understand that as subjects, we need to play safe.

374
00:33:45,963 --> 00:33:49,136
But now, I've endured so much hardship...

375
00:33:49,136 --> 00:33:51,759
to return to my rightful family with the Golden Scroll and Phoenix Seal.

376
00:33:51,759 --> 00:33:53,952
And here you are, trying so hard to stop me.

377
00:33:53,952 --> 00:33:57,399
Did Zongzheng Wuyou promise you anything in return?

378
00:33:57,399 --> 00:34:00,125
Or do you think that Zongzheng Wuyou...

379
00:34:00,125 --> 00:34:03,144
will return to this court?

380
00:34:03,144 --> 00:34:07,461
- Don't sling mud at me.
- Guards. Bring Sir Lin out for interrogation.

381
00:34:07,461 --> 00:34:10,730
Let's see how many traitors there are still.

382
00:34:10,730 --> 00:34:13,993
Fu Chou, you are just using this chance to get revenge.

383
00:34:13,993 --> 00:34:17,579
Your mother has only herself to blame... for her death.

384
00:34:17,579 --> 00:34:20,746
So, you've known from the start that I'm the son of Fu Yuan.

385
00:34:20,746 --> 00:34:22,765
- But you pretended to doubt me.
- You...

386
00:34:22,765 --> 00:34:26,625
I never thought that you'd really have an ulterior motive. Bring him away.

387
00:34:26,625 --> 00:34:29,948
Let go of me! Let go of me!

388
00:34:29,948 --> 00:34:33,510
Fu Chou, how daring of you.

389
00:34:36,130 --> 00:34:38,445
You are a traitor.

390
00:34:39,312 --> 00:34:42,092
What are you doing? You...

391
00:34:45,607 --> 00:34:51,187
My fellow officials, do any of you... have other objections?

392
00:34:53,440 --> 00:34:56,980
- Greetings, Your Highness.
- Stand up.

393
00:34:56,980 --> 00:34:59,262
Get up now!

394
00:34:59,262 --> 00:35:02,039
He is a traitor!

395
00:35:02,039 --> 00:35:04,981
You are a low-life. A traitor!

396
00:35:04,981 --> 00:35:08,214
Fu Chou. Fu Chou!

397
00:35:45,727 --> 00:35:48,085
Why did it become the real Rong Le?

398
00:35:49,960 --> 00:35:52,740
What do you mean?

399
00:35:52,740 --> 00:35:55,606
According to our initial plan,

400
00:35:55,606 --> 00:35:58,176
it was supposed to be Princess Rong Le.

401
00:35:58,176 --> 00:36:00,959
I've already asked Hen Xiang to replace her.

402
00:36:00,959 --> 00:36:05,599
Why would the real Rong Le be the one at the square?

403
00:36:05,599 --> 00:36:07,701
Did you put a spoke in my wheel?

404
00:36:07,701 --> 00:36:10,674
Did you?

405
00:36:10,674 --> 00:36:13,695
In order to protect Princess Rong Le,

406
00:36:13,695 --> 00:36:16,619
how could you ask Hen Xiang to take her place?

407
00:36:16,619 --> 00:36:19,805
I heard that the plan this time had gone very smoothly.

408
00:36:19,805 --> 00:36:22,099
I thought you'd already thought it through.

409
00:36:22,099 --> 00:36:26,120
I thought that you'd given up on love for the greater good.

410
00:36:28,481 --> 00:36:31,640
You said that you love her.

411
00:36:31,640 --> 00:36:35,680
But you didn't realize that she was the one at the square.

412
00:36:35,680 --> 00:36:40,810
Zongzheng Wuyou was able to identify her.

413
00:36:40,810 --> 00:36:43,899
That's why he surrendered willingly.

414
00:36:43,899 --> 00:36:46,440
You know it clearly yourself.

415
00:36:46,440 --> 00:36:48,599
If she were not the real Princess Rong Le,

416
00:36:48,599 --> 00:36:52,000
you wouldn't have been able to fool Zongzheng Wuyou so easily.

417
00:37:02,220 --> 00:37:04,260
All of you, get up!

418
00:37:09,705 --> 00:37:15,182
Congratulate our young master that he has gotten his revenge...

419
00:37:15,182 --> 00:37:17,811
and has completed a great cause!

420
00:37:17,811 --> 00:37:21,533
Congratulations for completing a great cause, Young Master!

421
00:37:46,220 --> 00:37:50,359
Everybody, evacuate at once.

422
00:37:50,359 --> 00:37:54,759
♫ I can't help but to ask after you ♫

423
00:37:54,759 --> 00:37:59,022
♫ Our hearts are a lifetime apart ♫

424
00:37:59,022 --> 00:38:03,805
♫ No one comes, also no one asks ♫

425
00:38:03,805 --> 00:38:07,699
♫ How do we keep living this life? ♫

426
00:38:07,699 --> 00:38:10,959
♫ Finally, I've learned how to trust ♫

427
00:38:10,959 --> 00:38:13,291
Wuyou!

428
00:38:16,390 --> 00:38:21,008
♫ We've thrown away fate that we'd received by chance ♫

429
00:38:21,008 --> 00:38:24,301
♫ I have to admit to my mistakes ♫

430
00:38:24,301 --> 00:38:28,699
♫ I regret the one mistake that I made so much ♫

431
00:38:28,699 --> 00:38:32,967
♫ All hope is lost, how do I start over? ♫

432
00:38:32,967 --> 00:38:37,151
♫ I cling to the past despite the pains ♫

433
00:38:37,151 --> 00:38:41,595
♫ I won't let our love be a regret ♫

434
00:38:41,595 --> 00:38:46,179
♫ Living without sorrow, dying without any hate ♫

435
00:38:46,179 --> 00:38:50,399
♫ This is the leniency that you've shown to me ♫

436
00:38:50,399 --> 00:38:54,260
♫ We are not holding hands, but you are holding my heart ♫

437
00:38:54,260 --> 00:38:55,960
[A Propitious Sky is Favorable for the Land]

438
00:38:55,960 --> 00:38:57,868
Why is the princess still unconscious?

439
00:38:57,868 --> 00:38:59,989
She has been unconscious for so long.

440
00:39:01,300 --> 00:39:05,800
♫ I've locked you in my heart and I've locked you in my dreams ♫

441
00:39:05,809 --> 00:39:07,740
Sir Xiao.

442
00:39:08,880 --> 00:39:12,480
She will be fine, right?

443
00:39:19,749 --> 00:39:23,154
- What are you doing?
- I'm going to kill him.

444
00:39:23,154 --> 00:39:25,255
Are you crazy?

445
00:39:25,255 --> 00:39:27,980
Ever since General Fu and princess came back to the manor,

446
00:39:27,980 --> 00:39:32,187
General Fu has sentenced all the guards in Tranquil Garden to death.

447
00:39:32,187 --> 00:39:35,268
Even Chang Jian is being punished.

448
00:39:35,268 --> 00:39:36,744
General Fu stood guard beside...

449
00:39:36,744 --> 00:39:39,778
the princess without rest,without drinking and without eating.

450
00:39:39,778 --> 00:39:41,918
If you barge in suddenly,

451
00:39:41,918 --> 00:39:43,965
you'll lose your life.

452
00:39:43,965 --> 00:39:46,506
As the princess's bodyguard,

453
00:39:46,506 --> 00:39:49,527
I've failed my duty for not being able to protect her well.

454
00:39:49,527 --> 00:39:53,679
Now... Now, she has already become like this.

455
00:39:53,679 --> 00:39:56,837
Am I not going to avenge her because I care for my own life?

456
00:39:56,837 --> 00:40:01,058
Xiao Sha, I feel the same as you.

457
00:40:01,058 --> 00:40:04,011
I'm very upset that she is hurt.

458
00:40:05,160 --> 00:40:07,168
But now, we are the only ones left...

459
00:40:07,168 --> 00:40:09,549
who are with the princess.

460
00:40:09,549 --> 00:40:12,074
If anything happens to us,

461
00:40:12,074 --> 00:40:14,792
who is going to protect her?

462
00:40:14,792 --> 00:40:17,440
Who is going to take care of her?

463
00:40:53,262 --> 00:40:55,042
You are awake.

464
00:41:02,060 --> 00:41:03,980
Where is Wuyou?

465
00:41:06,140 --> 00:41:09,000
Where is Wuyou? Tell me.

466
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:11,720
How is he now?

467
00:41:11,720 --> 00:41:13,855
You've been unconscious for two days.

468
00:41:14,913 --> 00:41:16,519
Don't think about other things.

469
00:41:16,519 --> 00:41:20,518
Get a good rest and let your body recover, all right?

470
00:41:26,200 --> 00:41:28,020
Don't touch me.

471
00:41:34,841 --> 00:41:39,050
I hate your face that faked innocence so much.

472
00:41:39,935 --> 00:41:43,010
You pretended to care about me,

473
00:41:43,010 --> 00:41:46,691
but you were actually plotting about how to use me.

474
00:41:46,691 --> 00:41:49,189
- I didn't do it.
- You didn't do what?

475
00:41:50,655 --> 00:41:54,747
You didn't use me to threaten Wuyou?

476
00:41:54,747 --> 00:41:58,286
You didn't personally feed me the toxin by force?

477
00:41:58,286 --> 00:42:01,262
Or you didn't send someone to bring me into the palace...

478
00:42:01,262 --> 00:42:03,675
so that I can be humiliated in public?

479
00:42:03,675 --> 00:42:05,662
I didn't know that she was you.

480
00:42:05,662 --> 00:42:10,000
If you don't want to tell me whether he lives or not, then leave.

481
00:42:11,562 --> 00:42:14,757
Now, I don't want to look at you at all.

482
00:42:14,757 --> 00:42:17,924
And I don't want to talk to you.

483
00:42:17,924 --> 00:42:20,129
You make me feel that...

484
00:42:20,129 --> 00:42:23,198
I'm a disaster to others as long as I'm still alive.

485
00:42:26,200 --> 00:42:28,909
Rong Le, let's not think about other things for now, all right?

486
00:42:28,909 --> 00:42:31,750
Where is Wuyou?

487
00:42:31,750 --> 00:42:34,161
I want to see him.

488
00:43:10,190 --> 00:43:13,730
♫ The snow falls on my palm ♫

489
00:43:13,730 --> 00:43:19,150
♫ I just want to gaze at you one more time ♫

490
00:43:19,150 --> 00:43:26,790
♫ I wait for the warmth of your gaze to melt it ♫

491
00:43:27,790 --> 00:43:32,350
♫ We are fated to get hurt from the moment we met each other ♫

492
00:43:32,350 --> 00:43:36,260
♫ I miss you but I can only gaze at you in silence ♫

493
00:43:36,260 --> 00:43:45,690
♫ You are keeping me out with your care
Although we are together, I feel lost ♫

494
00:43:45,690 --> 00:43:50,180
♫ I can wait for you until my hair turns white ♫

495
00:43:50,180 --> 00:43:54,900
♫ I can endure all the loneliness just for you ♫

496
00:43:54,900 --> 00:44:03,960
♫ I will be your hearth in the coldest of places ♫

497
00:44:03,960 --> 00:44:08,960
♫ For you, I am willing to suffer ♫

498
00:44:08,960 --> 00:44:13,200
♫ I want to ward off the coldness for you ♫

499
00:44:13,200 --> 00:44:21,370
♫ As long as I can be with you, I'm willing to give you all of me ♫

500
00:44:22,910 --> 00:44:28,050
♫ In a blink of an eye, my hair has turned silver ♫

501
00:44:28,050 --> 00:44:32,660
♫ I'm fated to live in loneliness without any regrets ♫

502
00:44:32,660 --> 00:44:41,730
♫ The winter may be cold,
but I will watch from afar and keep you warm ♫

503
00:44:41,730 --> 00:44:46,660
♫ I'm willing to wipe away your blood and wounds for you ♫

504
00:44:46,660 --> 00:44:50,900
♫ I'm willing to live in darkness for you ♫

